# Dar-Ul-Quran — Windsurf AI Rules

## Project Identity

Islamic educational organization website (Pakistan/Urdu-speaking audience). Stack: Next.js 15 App Router + React 19 + Sanity v6 CMS + Tailwind CSS v4 + TypeScript 6. Fully RTL, font: Noto Nastaliq Urdu.

---

## Architecture

```
app/
  layout.tsx              Root (RTL HTML lang="ur" dir="rtl")
  (site)/layout.tsx       Site shell — fetches siteSettings + headerNav from Sanity
  (site)/page.tsx         Homepage
  (site)/*/page.tsx       Static section pages
  (site)/articles/[slug]/ Article detail
  (site)/online-courses/[...slug]/  Hierarchical course (catch-all)
  (site)/services/[...slug]/        Hierarchical service (catch-all)
  api/contact/route.ts    POST: Sanity write + Gmail SMTP
  studio/[[...tool]]/     Embedded Sanity Studio

components/layout/        Header (4-level recursive nav), Footer
components/sections/      HeroSection, CarouselSection
components/ui/            Reveal, ContentCard, WhatsAppButton

sanity/lib/queries.ts     ALL GROQ — never inline in pages
sanity/lib/client.ts      safeFetch (null-safe)
sanity/lib/image.ts       urlFor()
sanity/schemaTypes/       Sanity schema definitions
```

