## Prohibited Patterns

| Pattern | Use Instead |
|---------|------------|
| `<a href>` | `<Link href>` from next/link |
| `<img src>` | `<Image>` from next/image |
| Inline GROQ strings | Export from queries.ts |
| `any` type | Proper types or `unknown` |
| `console.log` | Remove or use `console.error` in catch only |
| Hardcoded contacts | Fetch from Sanity siteSettings |
| `useEffect` for fetch | Async Server Component |
| `styled-components` | Tailwind classes only |
| `bg-opacity-50` | `bg-black/50` (Tailwind v4) |

