## Environment

```env
NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_PROJECT_ID  # Sanity project
NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_DATASET      # Usually: production
SANITY_API_TOKEN                # Write token for contact form
EMAIL_USER                      # Gmail sender
EMAIL_PASS                      # Gmail App Password
EMAIL_TO                        # Notification recipient
```

Never log, commit, or expose these values.

---

## Key Gotchas

- `[...slug]` params → `string[]`, always join for path reconstruction
- Sanity image CDN: `cdn.sanity.io` → `next.config.ts` remotePatterns required
- ISR 300s on layouts → nav CMS changes take up to 5 minutes
- Noto Nastaliq Urdu has tall ascenders — test all UI with real Urdu text, not Lorem Ipsum
- RTL flexbox: `flex-row` reverses visually — use `flex-row-reverse` or `rtl:flex-row-reverse` for LTR visual order when needed
